data.description: UPGRADE GALORE !!!This beautiful updated home has a great functional floor plan . Open layout with high ceiling in the living room. Kitchen has been remodeled completely with new cabinet , granite counter and back splash and new appliance .New paint through out the house .New floor is in living room, dining room and kitchen .New HVAC install in 2023 .Both bathrooms has a lot of upgrade with beautiful vanity sink ,quartz counter top ,new toilet and stunning tile floor. Back yard is a great size to play and host for a privet outdoor entertainment !Also installed water purifier . Seller Spent $70,000 to do all of these upgrades !!! This home is your ticket to a modern ,comfortable lifestyle !!
